modules.description: This module offers operations for creating, modifying, and transforming arrays with support for in-place updates, functional transformations, and memory-efficient slicing. It works with C-style arrays and Caml arrays, enabling direct element access, safe cross-array copying, and zero-allocation conversions between array representations. These capabilities are particularly useful for low-level array manipulation, numerical computations, and scenarios requiring seamless interoperability between different array formats.
